What we do
MINDSET® Integrated applies science-based analysis and expert guidance to aid in the objective understanding of brain health.

MINDSET® was created to bring brain injury science-based solutions from the research lab to the market in an approach that ensures accurate data collection, reliable data analysis, and objective results.

  • Objective analysis of brain health
  • Expert reviews
  • Comprehensive individual case consultation
  • Groundbreaking case record management
who we help
  • Legal Professionals
  • Physicians & Imaging Centers
  • Individuals

Legal teams benefit from our unique combination of scientific expertise and objective, data-driven assessments. Our comprehensive reports, based on cutting-edge MRI techniques and a robust reference database, provide clear, scientifically-validated evidence to support legal claims.
